<h4>Mailing Lists</h4>

<p>
Just click on the links to subscribe or unsubscribe. There's a link to the
list archive on the subscribe/unsubscribe pages. We don't link the archives
here because the link is going to change shortly (SourceForge will switch to
a new mail archiving system, ditching Geocrawler in the process).
</p>

<p>
<A HREF="http://lists.sourceforge.net/mailman/listinfo/gtk-gnutella-users/">gtk-gnutella-users</A>
Main list for Gtk-Gntuella users<br>

<A HREF="http://lists.sourceforge.net/mailman/listinfo/gtk-gnutella-devel/">gtk-gnutella-devel</A>
If you're interested in contributing to Gtk-Gnutella<br>

<A HREF="http://lists.sourceforge.net/mailman/listinfo/gtk-gnutella-announce/">gtk-gnutella-announce</A>
For releases announcements only<br>
</p>

<h4>IRC Chat</h4>

<p>
On the <a href="http://www.openprojects.net/">Open Projects Network</a> (short OPN) we meet in the
channel <a href="http://www.maol.ch/irc/egg2html.php?channel=gtk-gnutella">#gtk-gnutella</a>. There's always someone there, but not
everytime someone who know's the answer to your question.
</p>